rap|'''Ahmad Zahid Hamidi'''}}  ([[United Malays National Organisation|UMNO]])\n| rowspan=3 align=\"right\"|18,909\n| rowspan=3|51.37%\n|-\n|{{Party shading/Keadilan}} |\n|Pakhrurrazi Arshad ([[People's Justice Party (Malaysia)|PKR]])\n|align=\"right\" |13,836\n|37.59%\n| rowspan=3|37,620\n| rowspan=3|5,073\n| rowspan=3|79.89%\n|-\n|{{Party shading/PAS}} |\n|Ata Abdul Muneim Hasan Adli ([[Pan-Malaysian Islamic Party|PAS]])\n|align=\"right\" |4,061\n|11.03%\n|-\n|}\n\n== Honours ==\n* {{Flag|Kelantan}} :\n** [[File:MY-KEL Order of the Crown of Kelantan - Star of Muhammad.svg|50px]] Knight Commander of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Kelantan|Order of the Crown of Kelantan]] (DPMK) - '''Dato'''' (2005)<ref name=\":1\" /><ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]]|accessdate=25 October 2018|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2005/04/02/sultan-of-kelantan-birthday-honours-list/|title=Sultan of Kelantan birthday honours list|date=2 April 2005}}</ref>\n** [[File:My-KEL Order of the Life of the Crown of Kelantan 2006.svg|50px]] Knight Grand Commander of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Kelantan|Order of the Life of the Crown of Kelantan]] (SJMK) - '''Dato'''' (2009)<ref name=\":1\" /><ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]]|accessdate=25 October 2018|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2009/03/31/constitution-must-be-respected-says-kelantan-sultan/|work=[[Bernama]]|title=Constitution must be respected, says Kelantan Sultan|date=31 March 2009}}</ref>\n* {{Flag|Malacca}} :\n** [[File:MY-MAL Exalted Order of Malacca.svg|50px]] Companion Class I of the [[List of post-nominal letters (Malacca)|Exalted Order of Malacca]] (DMSM) - '''Datuk''' (1993)<ref name=\":1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.istiadat.gov.my/index.php/component/semakanlantikanskp/|title=SEMAKAN PENERIMA DARJAH KEBESARAN, BINTANG DAN PINGAT|publisher=[[Prime Minister's Department (Malaysia)]]|accessdate=25 October 2018}}</ref>\n** [[File:MY-MAL Exalted Order of Malacca.svg|50px]] Knight Grand Commander of the [[List of post-nominal letters (Malacca)|Exalted Order of Malacca]] (DUNM) - '''Datuk Seri Utama''' (2015)<ref name=\":1\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/2015/10/zahid-leads-malacca-honours-list|date=8 October 2015|accessdate=25 October 2018|publisher=[[New Straits Times]]|title=Zahid leads Malacca honours list|work=Roshidi Abu Samah}}</ref>\n* {{Flag|Pahang}} :\n** [[File:MY-PAH Order of Sultan Ahmad Shah of Pahang - Grand Knight - SSAP.svg|50px]] Grand Knight of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Pahang|Order of Sultan Ahmad Shah of Pahang]] (SSAP) - '''Dato' Sri''' (2008)<ref name=\":1\" /><ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]]|accessdate=12 October 2018|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2009/02/12/david-arumugam-khadijah-ibrahim-now-datuks/|work=[[Bernama]]|title=David Arumugam, Khadijah Ibrahim now Datuks|date=12 February 2009}}</ref>\n* {{Flag|Perak}} :\n** [[File:MY-PERA Order of the Perak State Crown - lower classes.svg|50px]] Knight Commander of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Perak|Order of the Perak State Crown]] (DPMP) - '''Dato'''' (2001)<ref name=\":1\" />\n** [[File:MY-PERA Order of the Perak State Crown - Kn Grd Commander - SPMP.svg|50px]] Knight Grand Commander of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Perak|Order of the Perak State Crown]] (SPMP) - '''Dato' Seri''' (2008)<ref name=\":1\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.malaysia-today.net/2008/04/19/perak-mb-to-be-awarded-datuk-seri-title/|date=19 April 2008|accessdate=8 September 2018|publisher=[[Malaysia Today]]|title=Perak MB To Be Awarded Datuk Seri Title|work=AdminK}}</ref>\n** Ordinary Class of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Perak|Perak Family Order of Sultan Nazrin Shah]] (SPSN) - '''Dato' Seri Di Raja''' (2015)<ref name=\":1\" />\n* {{Flag|Sabah}} :\n** [[File:MY-SAB Order of Kinabalu - SPDK.svg|50px]] Grand Commander of the [[Order of Kinabalu#Grand Commander|Order of Kinabalu]] (SPDK) - '''Datuk Seri Panglima''' (2011)<ref name=\":1\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theborneopost.com/2011/10/01/highest-state-award-for-eight/|date=1 October 2011|accessdate=14 September 2018|publisher=[[Borneo Post]]|title=Highest state award for eight|work=Sandra Sokial}}</ref>\n* {{Flag|Sarawak}} :\n** [[File:MY-SAR Order of the Star of Sarawak - 2 ribbon PNBS -JBS-PBS-ABS-BBS.svg|50px]] Knight Commander of the [[Most Exalted Order of the Star of Sarawak#Panglima Negara Bintang Sarawak (P.N.B.S.)|Order of the Star of Sarawak]] (PNBS) - '''Dato' Sri''' (2013)<ref name=\":1\" /><ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[Borneo Post]]|accessdate=25 October 2018|url=http://www.theborneopost.com/2013/09/14/muhyiddin-heads-list-of-tyt-birthday-award-recipients/|title=Muhyiddin heads list of TYT birthday award recipients|date=14 September 2013}}</ref>\n** [[File:MY-SAR Order of the Star of the Hornbill (Bintang Kenyalang) - 1. Knight Grand Commander (DP).svg|50px]] Knight Grand Commander of the [[Order of the Star of Hornbill Sarawak#Datuk Patinggi Bintang Kenyalang (D.P.)|Order of the Star of Hornbill Sarawak]] (DP) - '''Datuk Patinggi''' (2016)<ref name=\":1\" /><ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]]|accessdate=12 October 2018|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2016/09/09/zahid-heads-list-of-115-sarawak-state-award-recipients/|work=[[Bernama]]|title=Zahid heads list of 115 Sarawak state award recipients|date=9 September 2016}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n*[[Bagan Datok (federal constituency)]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Ahmad Zahid Hamidi}}\n* {{url|https://ahmadzahidhamidi.wordpress.com/|Official blog}} \n* {{facebook|zahidhamidi.fanpage}}\n* {{pom|3598}}\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{S-off}}\n|-\n{{S-bef|before=[[Wan Azizah Wan Ismail]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Leader of the Opposition (Malaysia)|Leader of the Opposition]]|years= 2018-2019}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Ismail Sabri Yaakob]]}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[